data.description: Awesome opportunity in a great location!  This 3 bed 2 bath home in desirable Pleasant Pointe has great space with freshly paint and new roof. The front entry opens to large living room with vaulted ceiling with gas fireplace! Kitchen includes pantry, dishwasher, stove/oven and microwave that leads into the breakfast area with lots of natural light with wainscoting & tray ceiling! Owner's suite has tray ceiling, upgraded ceiling fan, walk-in closet, double sink vanity, and separate tub and shower.  Great outdoor space w/screened porch off of the breakfast area and a large covered patio for entertaining with double ceiling fans and pull down shades!  This home qualifies for 100% financing, and includes a 1 year home warranty with approved offer!  schedule your showing today!
